TI  - Eradicating down the food chain: optimal multispecies eradication schedules for a commonly encountered invaded island ecosystem
T2  - JOURNAL OF APPLIED ECOLOGY
LA  - English
KW  - alien invasive species
KW  - decision theory
KW  - introduced species
KW  - optimal control strategy
