TI  - Prioritising the eradication of invasive species from island archipelagos with high reinvasion risk
T2  - JOURNAL OF APPLIED ECOLOGY
LA  - English
KW  - dynamic programming
KW  - invasive alien species
KW  - island eradications
KW  - reincursion
KW  - stochastic population modelling
