TI  - A value-based monitoring system to support heritage conservation planning
T2  - JOURNAL OF CULTURAL HERITAGE MANAGEMENT AND SUSTAINABLE DEVELOPMENT
LA  - English
KW  - Monitoring
KW  - Heritage planning
KW  - Heritage values
