TI  - Does insect trapping truly measure insect populations?
T2  - AGRICULTURAL AND FOREST ENTOMOLOGY
LA  - English
KW  - chromotropic traps
KW  - field survey
KW  - insect population dynamics
KW  - pheromone traps
