TI  - Consistency and use of information about threats in the participatory process for identification of priority conservation areas in the Brazilian Amazon
T2  - JOURNAL FOR NATURE CONSERVATION
LA  - English
KW  - Amazon
KW  - Threat
KW  - Conservation planning
KW  - Participatory decision-making
KW  - DEFORESTATION
