TI  - SAA-YOLO: A scale-aware attention enhanced YOLOv10 for UAV-based detection of medicinal plant Phlomoides rotata in alpine grasslands
T2  - COMPUTERS AND ELECTRONICS IN AGRICULTURE
LA  - English
KW  - UAV monitoring
KW  - Phlomoides rotata
KW  - Scale-aware deep learning
