TI  - Effects of Cropping Practices on Water-Use and Water Productivity of Dryland Winter Wheat in the High Plains Ecoregion of Wyoming
T2  - JOURNAL OF CROP IMPROVEMENT
LA  - English
KW  - conservation practices
KW  - DSSAT
KW  - no-till
