TI  - Ascertaining erosion potential of watersheds by utilizing Fuzzy Analytical Hierarchy Process (FAHP) and morphometric parameters of the Savitri River basin (Maharashtra), India
T2  - JOURNAL OF INDIAN GEOPHYSICAL UNION
LA  - English
KW  - Morphometric parameters
KW  - Prioritization
