TI  - A Modified PESTEL- and FCM-Driven Decision Support System to Mitigate the Extinction of Marine Species in the Mediterranean Sea
T2  - INFORMATION
LA  - English
KW  - ecological threats
KW  - biodiversity
KW  - conservation strategies
KW  - sealife
KW  - CLIMATE-CHANGE
KW  - BIODIVERSITY
