TI  - A ERSF-VIPA framework: scalable wildlife movement modelling for conflict mitigation
T2  - MOVEMENT ECOLOGY
LA  - English
KW  - Asian elephants (<italic>elephas maximus</italic>)
KW  - Enhanced resource selection function-vector network iterative pathfinding algorithm
KW  - Human-wildlife conflict
KW  - Limited data
KW  - Wildlife movement path prediction
