TI  - Emerging applications of large language models in ecology and conservation science
T2  - CONSERVATION BIOLOGY
LA  - English
KW  - BERT
KW  - ChatGPT
KW  - DeepSeek
KW  - foundation models
KW  - generative AI
KW  - LLMs
