TI  - RUSLE modeling and spatial approach in soil erosion-prone areas for erosion rate prediction and strengthening land use planning in the Battang River basin, Palopo City
T2  - PROGRESS IN DISASTER SCIENCE
LA  - English
KW  - Soil Erosion
