TI  - Optimal Ecohydraulic Design of Fish Habitat in Canal under Ambiguity in Preference Curve
T2  - PROCEEDINGS OF THE 35TH IAHR WORLD CONGRESS, VOLS I AND II
LA  - English
CP  - 35th World Congress of the International-Association-for-Hydro-Environment-Engineering-and-Research (IAHR)
