TI  - Comparing support vector machines and k-nearest neighbors for Eucalyptus tree identification using bark images
T2  - EURO-MEDITERRANEAN JOURNAL FOR ENVIRONMENTAL INTEGRATION
LA  - English
KW  - Data collection
KW  - Features extraction
KW  - Bark images
KW  - Remote sensing
