TI  - A parcel-based graph to match connectivity analysis with field action in agricultural landscapes: Is node removal a reliable method?
T2  - LANDSCAPE AND URBAN PLANNING
LA  - English
KW  - Agricultural parcel
KW  - Landscape connectivity
KW  - Connectivity metric
KW  - Prioritization
