TI  - Accelerating marine spatial planning in the Western Pacific region: Current status and future directions
T2  - OCEAN & COASTAL MANAGEMENT
LA  - English
KW  - Marine spatial planning
KW  - Priority areas
KW  - Western Pacific
KW  - Acceleration
KW  - Bibliometric analysis
