TI  - APPLYING INSTREAM FLOW INCREMENTAL METHOD FOR THE SPAWNING HABITAT PROTECTION OF CHINESE STURGEON (Acipenser sinensis)
T2  - RIVER RESEARCH AND APPLICATIONS
LA  - English
