TI  - Assessment of sugar beet lime measure efficiency for soil contamination in a Mediterranean Ecosystem. The case study of Guadiamar Green Corridor (SW Spain)
T2  - CATENA
LA  - English
KW  - Soil contamination
KW  - Trace elements
