TI  - A GMOP-PLUS-InVEST-GWR Coupled Model for Simulating "Production-Living-Ecological" Functions and Carbon Stock Dynamics in the Chengdu Metropolitan Area
T2  - LAND
LA  - English
KW  - ecosystem carbon stocks
KW  - GMOP model
KW  - GWR model
KW  - multi-scenario simulation
