TI  - A multifaceted approach in leveraging electronic health record tools for safe inpatient use of concentrated U-500 insulin
T2  - AMERICAN JOURNAL OF HEALTH-SYSTEM PHARMACY
LA  - English
KW  - diabetes
KW  - electronic health record
KW  - informatics
KW  - insulin
