TI  - Sharing or sparing? An analysis of the forest owners' opportunity costs in cultural ecosystem services accounting for the Via Transilvanica outdoor recreational trail
T2  - NOTULAE BOTANICAE HORTI AGROBOTANICI CLUJ-NAPOCA
LA  - English
KW  - cultural ecosystem services
KW  - decision support system
