KW  - Farming systems
KW  - Sustainable practices
KW  - Participatory co-development
KW  - Soil health
KW  - Malawi
KW  - CONSERVATION AGRICULTURE SYSTEMS
KW  - MAIZE
KW  - PRODUCTIVITY
KW  - INNOVATION
