TI  - Economic prosperity and ecological sustainability strategy for fishing violations hotspots
T2  - GLOBAL JOURNAL OF ENVIRONMENTAL SCIENCE AND MANAGEMENT-GJESM
LA  - English
KW  - Economic risk mapping
KW  - Fisheries enforcement
