TI  - Integrated remote sensing and GIS based spatial modelling through analytical hierarchy process (AHP) for water logging hazard, vulnerability and risk assessment in Keleghai river basin, India
T2  - MODELING EARTH SYSTEMS AND ENVIRONMENT
LA  - English
KW  - Command areas
KW  - Geographical information system
KW  - Ground water table
KW  - Hazard
KW  - NDMI
KW  - NDVI
KW  - NDWI
