KW  - Vulnerability
KW  - Water-logged areas
KW  - FLOOD HAZARD
KW  - LIQUID WATER
KW  - INDEX NDWI
KW  - VEGETATION
KW  - SALINITY
KW  - REFLECTANCE
KW  - REGION
