TI  - Simulating soil-carbon-water interactions in two profiles to select precision cover for soil-health and drought-resilience
T2  - SMART AGRICULTURAL TECHNOLOGY
LA  - English
KW  - Soil organic carbon
KW  - Clay+silt content
